oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Various Country Music Fan Fair promotional radio spots from 1972, featuring Buck Owens, Roy Clark, Lynn Anderson, Chet Atkins, Glen Sherley, Stonewall Jackson, Hank Snow, Jan Howard, Bill Anderson, Danny Davis, Tommy Overstreet, Porter Wagoner, Waylon Jennings, Dickey Lee, and Darryl Reeves.
